text: Farmway LRT Station is a light rail transit station in Sengkang, Singapore. It opened on November 15 2007. It is part of the Sengkang LRT Line. ==Name== Its name was from the old roads near the station. ==Timeline== *November 15 2007 The station opened. ==Sources== ==Other websites== SBS Transit Website Category:Sengkang Category:Light Rail Transit (Singapore) stations
title: Farmway LRT Station
